    <item>
      <title>中国重大立法会议的五个要点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/china-npc-2024-key-takeaways-from-xi-consolidating-power-to-fiscal-stimulus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着国家主席习近平的权力日益集中，中国希望避免增长放缓，并将其经济转型为由技术创新驱动的经济。这是本月全国人民代表大会的要点，这是一年一度的立法会议，中国的橡皮图章议会将批准执政的共产党的政策。以下是该活动揭示的未来一年国家经济和政治方向的概要。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/china-npc-2024-key-takeaways-from-xi-consolidating-power-to-fiscal-stimulus</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 09:30:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于通胀回落仍然脆弱，欧洲央行卡齐米尔支持六月降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/ecb-s-kazimir-favors-june-cut-as-inflation-retreat-still-fragile</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行理事会成员彼得·卡齐米尔表示，欧洲央行不应在 6 月之前降低利率，因为官员需要更多数据来确保通胀得到抑制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/ecb-s-kazimir-favors-june-cut-as-inflation-retreat-still-fragile</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 09:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>黑胶唱片在缺席 32 年后重返英国通胀篮子</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/vinyl-records-back-in-uk-inflation-basket-after-32-year-absence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黑胶唱片人气飙升，32年来首次重返英国通胀篮子，而随着疫情从英国人的购物习惯中消失，洗手液也不再被纳入英国通胀篮子。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/vinyl-records-back-in-uk-inflation-basket-after-32-year-absence</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 09:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织总裁格奥尔基耶娃赢得德国支持连任</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/imf-chief-georgieva-wins-german-backing-for-a-second-term</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国财政部长克里斯蒂安·林德纳表示，克里斯塔利娜·格奥尔基耶娃“完全是领导国际货币基金组织的合适人选”，并公开承认德国对连任的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/imf-chief-georgieva-wins-german-backing-for-a-second-term</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 09:28:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯任命经纪人与外国人进行冻结资产交换</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/russia-appoints-broker-for-frozen-assets-swap-with-foreigners</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯任命了一名经纪人，在俄罗斯和因入侵乌克兰后实施的国际制裁而陷入困境的外国投资者之间进行资产互换。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/russia-appoints-broker-for-frozen-assets-swap-with-foreigners</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 09:26:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行不再购买 ETF，引发政策动向猜测</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/boj-refrains-from-etf-buying-stokes-policy-change-speculation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行周一没有涉足股市，这出人意料地背离了其通常在早盘股市下跌 2% 或以上时买入交易所交易基金的策略。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/boj-refrains-from-etf-buying-stokes-policy-change-speculation</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 08:44:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于中国库存堆积，铁矿石跌幅自 2022 年以来最大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/iron-ore-woes-deepen-as-inventories-in-china-keep-piling-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[铁矿石暴跌7%——跌破每吨 110 美元大关——中国的需求令人失望，导致市场库存膨胀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-11/iron-ore-woes-deepen-as-inventories-in-china-keep-piling-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Mar 2024 03:37:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
