      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-10/bond-investors-are-lining-up-to-fund-the-war-against-putin</link>
      <description><![CDATA[债券投资者敦促争论不休的欧盟领导人在国防支出问题上共同采取行动，并使欧盟的万亿欧元债券计划永久化。]]></description>
